	XFrom
	X.pg
	XThe
	X.hf From
	Xline contains the electronic mailing address of the person who sent the message,
	Xin the ARPA internet syntax.
	XIt may optionally also contain the full name of the person,
	Xin parentheses,
	Xafter the electronic address.
	XThe electronic address is the same as the entity responsible
	Xfor originating the article,
	Xunless the
	X.hf Sender
	Xheader is present,
	Xin which case the
	X.hf From
	Xheader might not be verified.
	XNote that in all site and domain names,
	Xupper and lower case are considered the same,
	Xthus
