	XThe full name is not considered a comment,
	Xbut an optional part of the header line.
	XEither the full name is omitted, 
	Xor it appears in parentheses after the electronic address
	Xof the person posting the article,
	Xor it appears before an electronic address enclosed in angle brackets.
